    "longDescription": "AI Mobile turns Codex into a goal-driven local resource orchestrator for Windows. It passively inventories available platforms and models, preserves unknown capacity honestly, builds a dependency-aware work graph, selects resources by capability, quality, capacity, speed, cost, and continuity, dispatches CLI workers, records compact per-run telemetry, and performs one bounded failover when justified. Codex remains the goal owner, critic, integrator, and final verifier. Antigravity desktop is used only when visible project, chat, model, or composer state is required.",
